Faint Blue line at Control position even after addition of samples and assay buffer

Invalid. Take a new cassette packaging and repeat the test.
strings.page_2:
NO Pink Purple line at ‘C’ (=control)

Invalid. Take a new cassette packaging and repeat the test.
strings.page_3:
Pink Purple Line at ‘C’ and NO other line

Negative
strings.page_4:
Pink Purple Line at ‘C’ AND at ‘Pf’

Positive for P. falciparum
strings.page_5:
Pink Purple Line at ‘C’, at ‘Pf’ AND at ‘Pv’

Positive for as a mixed infection with P. falciparum and P. vivax
strings.page_6:
Pink Purple Line at ‘C’ AND at ‘Pv’

Positive for P. vivax
